{"ts":"2026-06-06T12:27:16.360Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-06T12:27:16.360Z","author":"codex-search-vector-bundle","text":"Implementation + verification evidence (combined bundle pm-usw2 + pm-7tsx):\n\nCode/config/runtime:\n- Added vector_store.collection_name default + normalization + nested config alias (vector_store_collection_name) and wired collection/table naming through Qdrant/LanceDB targets + local LanceDB reset/query/upsert/delete paths.\n- Added search.query_expansion + search.rerank settings blocks (defaults, validator, serializer, nested aliases, CLI help surface) and built provider abstraction with extension override hooks.\n- Integrated query expansion + rerank in search pipeline with graceful fallback warnings; result filters now expose query_expansion_* + rerank_* fields.\n\nVerification gates:\n- pnpm build: pass\n- Focused tests for touched modules: pass\n- node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage: pass (100% lines/statements/branches/functions)\n- pnpm quality:static: pass\n- pnpm audit --prod: pass (no vulnerabilities)\n- pnpm changelog:pm:check: pass (pm-changelog 2026.6.6 installed; CHANGELOG unchanged/check mode passed)\n- pnpm contracts:update + pnpm contracts:check: pass (tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json refreshed)\n\nManual temp-dir smoke (isolated tracker):\n- Temp root: /tmp/tmp.7JsgtwmsaM\n- Initialized tracker + installed built-in search-advanced package.\n- Created items, configured:\n  - vector_store_adapter=lancedb\n  - vector_store_collection_name=smoke_collection\n  - lancedb_path=/tmp/tmp.7JsgtwmsaM/vector-store\n  - search query-expansion/rerank knobs enabled + configured\n- Reindex keyword: pass\n- Search keyword: pass (2 expected results)\n- Search semantic + hybrid with intentionally unreachable OpenAI endpoint:\n  - command degraded to keyword mode without hard failure\n  - warnings emitted as expected (query expansion provider unavailable + semantic/hybrid connection fallback)\n  - filters payload surfaced query_expansion_* and rerank_* fields\n\nTelemetry + Sentry validation:\n- pm telemetry status/stats/flush (repo default paths) executed successfully.\n- Flush drained queue to zero with successful timestamps.\n- Sentry MCP checks:\n  - Auth OK (whoami)\n  - org/project resolved: unbrained / pm-cli\n  - recent data available:\n    - errors dataset returned recent events\n    - logs dataset returned recent entries (including 2026-06-06 timestamps)\n  - spans query for last 24h returned no results (not a tooling failure); dataset attribute validation reports 403-limited scope but event/log retrieval works."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-06T12:27:16.360Z"}],"before_hash":"655e800806bdda9700f4c65648630dbdf62ca5b887f59263b325adc57274fb35","after_hash":"0f1618c246746c5a178ae5a41b71f002e6fb6000a548837582b0784bfab605c8"}
